{
  "stem": "13141.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to walk about half a block-- run half a block to the air-raid shelter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were sitting there with the gentiles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In one corner, we were sitting, I mean, not because they told us we should sit in the corner, but we just felt that way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were-- there were bombs falling, not too many in Stuttgart at a time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we sent that letter out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we must have sent, I would say, between 40 and 60 letters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what year was this in?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in-- that must have been at the end of 1940, I would say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we got three or four responses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of them, they didn't even answer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the three or four responses we got, we got-- three said they are very sorry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They can't do anything for us presently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was one in Bremen, a letter which told us that if we would bring valid passports to Bremen that he might be able to do something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We should bring two photographs and birth certificates, et cetera, et cetera, which we did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, this was a, a black consul of Liberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he, he told us-- we had talked to him on the phone before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He told us, now, I can give you the visa for Liberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I cannot give you the landing permit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The landing permit is up to the Department of the Interior.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that you cannot get.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just forget about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I can give you a visa, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Don't even apply for a landing permit, he said, because you won't have a chance.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
